```plantuml
@startuml alanchn31_Movalytics-Data-Warehouse

actor User
participant "Airflow Scheduler" as Scheduler
participant "BashOperator" as BashOp
participant "Spark Job" as Spark
participant "Redshift" as Redshift
participant "DataQualityOperator" as DQOp

User -> Scheduler: Triggers DAG execution
Scheduler -> BashOp: Execute data extraction (Kaggle/FRED)
BashOp -> Spark: Invoke Spark job (load_staging_*.py)
Spark -> Redshift: Load raw data to staging tables
Scheduler -> BashOp: Execute transformation scripts
BashOp -> Spark: Process staging data
Spark -> Redshift: Upsert to dimension tables
Scheduler -> DQOp: Run data quality checks
DQOp -> Redshift: Execute validation queries
Redshift --> DQOp: Return check results
DQOp --> Scheduler: Report quality status

@enduml
```